{"tid":476833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"e加d小朋友把口","createTime":"2017-11-22T11:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T11:39:09.000Z","uid":157710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f447137a30870fb5db4f172c88f2f29d5305ad3e","tid":476833,"uid":157710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:23:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的！今日同兩個小朋友踢波（番屋企期間見到），唔識佢地。當然我球技差踢咗個波入草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，當然我踢我汁番。<br />\n我話換番條長褲先搵，果兩個小朋友就硬係跟住我，其中一個小朋友見到我屋企就講&ldquo;點解你屋企咁鬼窮，咁鬼細&rdquo;，然後係我搵波期間就係咁串我窮，又煩住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係容忍都有限度，火都黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。大佬你老豆老母有錢大撚哂咩，我夠想我老豆係李家誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:粒波唔係佢。"},{"pid":"75fc4a3a24d9d730effb40a122e6887b6ce488d8","tid":476833,"uid":130320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:32:14.000Z","msg":"徙置區？"},{"pid":"38209c34bc4b56c93060cacfcc82ac743c497ea4","tid":476833,"uid":157710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>徙置區？</blockquote><br />\n鐵皮屋"}]}